for you

py-ipfs-api: https://github.com/ipfs/py-ipfs-api
pip install ipfsapi


web3.py(A python interface for interacting with the Ethereum blockchain and ecosystem):https://github.com/ethereum/web3.py


project structure
-- app
	-- models 					// data model entity
		models.py
	-- utils  					// utility tools 
		*.py
	-- views  					// controllers
		*Ctrl.py  				// controller handler
		views.py  				// router config
	-- static 					// static files
		-- css
		-- js
	-- templates 				// html files
		base.html 				// base.html is the skeleton of every page
		*.html
	config.py
	db_create.py 				// run this to init db
	run.py
